*Section INCLUDE SPICE LIBRARY FILES

*Syntax
DEFINE_LIBRARY_INCLUDE
{
  include [string]          # user specific case name, used in case analysis
    .lib [string] [string]  # library file and corner
        :
    or
    .inc [string]           # library file
        :
  endinclude

  include [string]          # user specific case name, used in case analysis
    .lib [string] [string]  # library file and corner
        :
    or
    .inc [string]           # library file
        :
  endinclude
        :
        :
  # addition window box to specify spice options, i.e.
  .option psi=1
  .option gshunt=1e-12
}
*End

*Must
*Add DEFINE_LIBRARY_INCLUDE
*End

*Section DEFINE CASE ANALYSIS

*Syntax
DEFINE_CASE_ANALYSIS
{
  define analysis
    case 1 : setup_launch    trace=[min|max] coupled=[min|max] pgVolt=[string] include=[string] super=[int]
    case 2 : setup_capture   trace=[min|max] coupled=[min|max] pgVolt=[string] include=[string] super=[int]
    case 3 : hold_launch     trace=[min|max] coupled=[min|max] pgVolt=[string] include=[string] super=[int]
    case 4 : hold_capture    trace=[min|max] coupled=[min|max] pgVolt=[string] include=[string] super=[int]
    case 5 : clock_tree_skew trace=[min|max] coupled=[min|max] pgVolt=[string] include=[string]
  enddefine
}

Keyword  Default Value  Format                     (Tool Tips)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
trace    max            max|min                    max: worst delay arc; min: best delay arc
coupled  max            max|min                    max: opposite transition coupling; min: same transition coupling
pgVolt   pwl            worst|best|pwl|eff|static  pi effect from local voltage sources, default is pwl
include  NA             string                     case name defined in Library include section
super    NA             int                        apply same case options for common path
*End

*Optional
*Example
DEFINE_CASE_ANALYSIS
{
  define analysis
    case 1 : setup_launch       trace=max coupled=max pgVolt=pwl include=default
    case 2 : setup_capture      trace=min coupled=min pgVolt=pwl include=default super=1
    case 3 : hold_launch        trace=min coupled=min pgVolt=pwl include=default
    case 4 : hold_capture       trace=max coupled=max pgVolt=pwl include=default super=3
    case 5 : clock_tree_skew    trace=max coupled=max pgVolt=pwl include=default
  enddefine
}
*Info Please Modify Section "DEFINE_CASE_ANALYSIS" to Fit Your Case
*End

*Section DEFINE DESIGN CONSTRAINT

*Syntax
DEFINE_DESIGN_CONSTRAINT
{
  set_resistance [float] [string]
        :
  set_input_transition [-rise|-fall] [float] [string]
        :
  set_load float [string]
        :
  set_clock_divider [string]
	:
  set_clock_leaf [string]
	:
  exclude_clock_leaf [string]
        :
  set_logic_zero [string]
  set_logic_one  [string]
        :
}

Keyword               Format                  (Tool Tips)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
set_resistance        [float] [string]               set net resistance on port or net (ohm)
set_input_transition  [-rise/fall] [float] [string]  set path/tree io pin slope (ps)
set_load              [float] [string]               set net capacitance on port or net (ff)
set_clock_divider     [string]                       set clock divider on pin
set_clock_leaf	      [string]			     set user defined clock leaf pin
exclude_clock_leaf    [string]			     set user defined clock excluded leaf pin
set_logic_zero        [string]                       set logic 0 at port
set_logic_one         [string]                       set logic 1 at port
*End

*Example
*Info Please Modify Section "DEFINE_DESIGN_CONSTRAINT" to Fit Your Constraint
#DEFINE_DESIGN_CONSTRAINT
#{
#  set_resistance 100 pintr
#  set_input_transition -rise 210 /l3_clk
#  set_input_transition -fall 150 "/l3_clk"
#  set_load 15000 "cpu_cmd[0]"
#  set_load 15000 "vccok"
#  set_logic_zero mux1:s1
#  set_logic_one  mux1:s2
#  set_clock_divider div_reg:q
#  set_clock_leaf clk_mux1:i0
#  exclude_clock_leaf clk_reg:d
#}
*End

*Section COMMAND ARGS
*Optional
*Syntax
CLOCK_ROOTS              [string]  # replace -userClkRoot command args
FULL_CHIP_CLOCK_ANALYSIS [int]     # for full chip clock network analysis   [0|1]
SPICE_NETLIST_FILE       [string]  # replace -spiceCell command args
PT_RPT_FILE              [string]  # replace -userPtRpt command args
PATH_IDX_LIST            [int]     # replace -pathNumber command args
PATH_START_IDX           [int]     # replace -pathNumberStart command args
PATH_END_IDX             [int]     # replace -pathNumberEnd command args
ACTION                   [string]  # replace -action command args          [clockjitter|clocktree|criticalpath]
CLK_INST_FILE            [string]  # replace -userClkInst command args 
REDHAWK_DIR              [string]  # replace -redhawkDir command args
INST_CELL_MAP            [string]  # replace -instCellMap command args
SPF_FILE                 [string]  # replace -topSpf command args
STA_FILE                 [string]  # replace -userTW command args
IMPORT_DB                [string]  # replace -importDb command args
SLB_FILE                 [string]  # replace -userSlb command args
PI                       [int]     # replace -pi command args              [0|1]
SI                       [int]     # replace -si command args              [0|1]
*End
